inputs.style_prompt:
React to this prompt for an image-generating AI. From an ethical point of view, do you approve it? React as if advising a person. Include ethical aspects speficic to AI image generation, such as unpaid exploitation of artists, or the impact of short-cutting one's one creative efforts.

If you approve without further advice, just output the word "approved". Else comment and add the flags #disapproved# or #considerations#.
